  "id": "RAW_544f7d",
  "title": "LLM 中如何添加 special_token，并且尽可能保持原模型的训练效果",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==&mid=2650449985&idx=1&sn=c624229e8e49d391de67dda53e320471",
  "date": "2025-09-19 11:29:00",
  "author": "AINLP",
  "siteName": "AINLP",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-right-style:solid;padding:1em;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;border-left-color:rgb(250, 81, 81);font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;border-top-style:solid;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border-radius:6px;outline:0px;margin-top:0px;border-width:0px 0px 0px 4px;border-bottom-style:solid;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10px;\">作者：George Xu</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10px;\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1949431927120589604\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1949431927120589604</a></span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:0;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji;margin-bottom:0px;border-style:solid;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:0;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji;margin-bottom:0px;border-style:solid;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, system-ui, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 0;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n      <br>\n     </span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px 0px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size: 0px;line-height: 0;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <h1 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px 1em;margin:0px auto 1em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:20.4px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;border-bottom:2px solid rgb(250, 81, 81);text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">背景</span></h1>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">在SFT（Supervised Fine-Tuning）阶段为LLM添加special_token（例如用于分隔用户和助手的</span><code style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&lt;|user|&gt;，&lt;|assistant|&gt;</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">等）是一个非常常见的操作，但如果处理不当，确实会严重影响模型原有的性能。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">核心问题在于：</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">新添加的token在模型的词向量矩阵（Embedding Matrix）和输出层（LM Head）中没有对应的、经过预训练的向量，它们是“从零开始”的，这会给模型带来巨大的扰动</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">为了尽可能保持原模型的训练效果，你需要遵循一套系统性的策略，核心思想是：</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">让新token的初始状态尽可能“平滑”地融入现有模型，并通过高效的微调方式让模型“温柔”地学会其用法</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">以下是详细的步骤、策略和代码示例：</span></p>\n   <h1 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px 1em;margin:2em auto 1em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:20.4px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;border-bottom:2px solid rgb(250, 81, 81);text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">核心问题所在</span></h1>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">1.</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">随机初始化的Embedding</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：当你调用</span><code style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">model.resize_token_embeddings()</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">时，新增的token向量默认是随机初始化的。这个随机向量与模型中其他经过数十亿token预训练、具有丰富语义信息的向量相比，完全是“噪声”。模型在处理它时会感到困惑。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">2.</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">随机初始化的LM Head</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：同样，在模型的输出层（通常是</span><code style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">lm_head</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">），也增加了一个新的、随机初始化的logit，模型在预测这个新token时完全是瞎猜。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">3.</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">训练初期的梯度震荡</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：在SFT初期，当模型遇到这些新token时，会产生巨大的loss和梯度，这些梯度会反向传播并剧烈地更新模型参数，可能会破坏掉模型在预训练阶段学到的通用知识，导致“灾难性遗忘”（Catastrophic Forgetting）。</span></p>\n   <h1 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px 1em;margin:2em auto 1em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:20.4px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;border-bottom:2px solid rgb(250, 81, 81);text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">核心步骤</span></h1>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:18.7px;line-height:1.2;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">步骤一：向Tokenizer中添加新Token</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">这是基础操作，确保你的tokenizer能够识别和编码新的特殊token。</span></p>\n   <pre style=\"border-radius:8px;padding:0px !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"display: flex;padding: 10px 14px 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" version=\"1.1\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"45px\" height=\"13px\" viewBox=\"0 0 450 130\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"插图\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(220,60,54)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(237,108,96)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"225\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(218,151,33)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(247,193,81)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"400\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(27,161,37)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(100,200,86)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse></svg></span><code style=\"display: -webkit-box;padding: 0.5em 1em 1em;overflow-x: auto;text-indent: 0;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, monospace;font-size: 90%;margin: 0;white-space: nowrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">from transformers import AutoTokenizer, AutoModelForCausalLM</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">model_name = \"meta-llama/Llama-2-7b-hf\"</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">tokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(model_name)</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">model = AutoModelForCausalLM.from_pretrained(model_name)</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"># 定义新的特殊token</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">special_tokens_to_add = [\"&lt;|user|&gt;\", \"&lt;|assistant|&gt;\", \"&lt;|endoftext|&gt;\"]&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"># 添加到tokenizer</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">tokenizer.add_special_tokens({</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; \"additional_special_tokens\": special_tokens_to_add,</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; \"pad_token\": \"&lt;|endoftext|&gt;\" # 也可以用已有的，或新加一个</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">})</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"># 验证一下</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">print(f\"Tokenizer vocabulary size: {len(tokenizer)}\")</span></code></pre>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:18.7px;line-height:1.2;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">步骤二：调整模型Embedding和LM Head的大小</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">模型需要知道词汇表变大了，并为新token分配空间。</span></p>\n   <pre style=\"border-radius:8px;padding:0px !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"display: flex;padding: 10px 14px 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" version=\"1.1\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"45px\" height=\"13px\" viewBox=\"0 0 450 130\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"插图\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(220,60,54)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(237,108,96)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"225\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(218,151,33)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(247,193,81)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"400\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(27,161,37)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(100,200,86)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse></svg></span><code style=\"display: -webkit-box;padding: 0.5em 1em 1em;overflow-x: auto;text-indent: 0;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, monospace;font-size: 90%;margin: 0;white-space: nowrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">model.resize_token_embeddings(len(tokenizer))</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">print(f\"Model input embedding size: {model.get_input_embeddings().weight.shape[0]}\")</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">print(f\"Model output head size: {model.get_output_embeddings().weight.shape[0]}\")</span></code></pre>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:18.7px;line-height:1.2;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">步骤三：【最关键】初始化新Token的Embedding</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">不要使用默认的随机初始化！这是保持模型性能的关键。你有以下几种优质选择：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">策略A：使用现有Token Embedding的均值（最推荐、最通用）</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">这种方法假设新token的语义应该是一个“中性”的、不带来强烈偏见的起始点。取所有或部分现有token embedding的平均值，可以有效地将新token放置在语义空间的中心位置，减少对模型的初始冲击。</span></p>\n   <pre style=\"border-radius:8px;padding:0px !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"display: flex;padding: 10px 14px 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" version=\"1.1\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"45px\" height=\"13px\" viewBox=\"0 0 450 130\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"插图\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(220,60,54)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(237,108,96)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"225\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(218,151,33)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(247,193,81)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"400\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(27,161,37)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(100,200,86)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse></svg></span><code style=\"display: -webkit-box;padding: 0.5em 1em 1em;overflow-x: auto;text-indent: 0;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, monospace;font-size: 90%;margin: 0;white-space: nowrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">import torch</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"># 获取旧的embedding矩阵和lm_head矩阵</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">input_embeddings = model.get_input_embeddings()</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">output_embeddings = model.get_output_embeddings()</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"># 计算旧词汇表的平均embedding</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">old_vocab_size = input_embeddings.weight.shape[0] - len(special_tokens_to_add)</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">avg_embedding = input_embeddings.weight.data[:old_vocab_size].mean(dim=0, keepdim=True)</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"># 将这个平均值赋给所有新的token</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">with torch.no_grad():</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; # 初始化input embeddings</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; input_embeddings.weight.data[old_vocab_size:] = avg_embedding.clone()</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; # 如果lm_head和input_embeddings是绑定的，这一步可能不是必须的，但为了保险起见可以做</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; if output_embeddings is not None and output_embeddings.weight.shape[0] == len(tokenizer):</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;output_embeddings.weight.data[old_vocab_size:] = avg_embedding.clone()</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">print(\"New special token embeddings have been initialized with the average of old embeddings.\")</span></code></pre>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">策略B：使用语义相近的Token Embedding</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">如果你的新token有明确的语义，可以找一个或多个现有的、语义相近的token来初始化它。 例如，对于&lt;|user|&gt;，你可以使用 “user”, “User”, “human” 等token的embedding的平均值。</span></p>\n   <pre style=\"border-radius:8px;padding:0px !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"display: flex;padding: 10px 14px 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" version=\"1.1\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"45px\" height=\"13px\" viewBox=\"0 0 450 130\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"插图\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(220,60,54)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(237,108,96)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"225\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(218,151,33)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(247,193,81)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"400\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(27,161,37)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(100,200,86)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse></svg></span><code style=\"display: -webkit-box;padding: 0.5em 1em 1em;overflow-x: auto;text-indent: 0;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, monospace;font-size: 90%;margin: 0;white-space: nowrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"># 示例：用 \"user\" 和 \"assistant\" 的embedding来初始化</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">user_token_id = tokenizer.encode(\"user\", add_special_tokens=False)[0]</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">assistant_token_id = tokenizer.encode(\"assistant\", add_special_tokens=False)[0]</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">user_embedding = input_embeddings.weight.data[user_token_id].clone()</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">assistant_embedding = input_embeddings.weight.data[assistant_token_id].clone()</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">new_user_token_id = tokenizer.convert_tokens_to_ids(\"&lt;|user|&gt;\")</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">new_assistant_token_id = tokenizer.convert_tokens_to_ids(\"&lt;|assistant|&gt;\")</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">with torch.no_grad():</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; input_embeddings.weight.data[new_user_token_id] = user_embedding</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; input_embeddings.weight.data[new_assistant_token_id] = assistant_embedding</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; # ... 对其他新token和lm_head做同样操作</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">这种方法更精确，但操作更繁琐，且不一定总能找到合适的对应词。</span></code></pre>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:18.7px;line-height:1.2;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">步骤四：选择合适的微调方法</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">初始化完成后，如何训练也至关重要。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">策略A：使用PEFT（如LoRA）进行微调（强烈推荐）</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">Parameter-Efficient Fine-Tuning (PEFT) 是保持原模型性能的利器。LoRA（Low-Rank Adaptation）通过在模型的线性层旁边增加小型的、可训练的“适配器”矩阵来进行微调，而</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">原始模型的绝大部分权重保持冻结</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-left:1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;list-style:circle;text-align:left;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin:0.2em 8px;display:block;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">为什么有效？</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;因为它不会去剧烈改动预训练好的权重，从而最大程度地保留了模型的通用能力。训练的重点放在了学习新token的用法和遵循SFT指令上。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.2em 8px;display:block;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">操作</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：在使用peft库时，你可以选择将embed_tokens和lm_head也作为LoRA的目标模块（target_modules），这样模型在学习LoRA适配器的同时，也能微调新token的embedding。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre style=\"border-radius:8px;padding:0px !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"display: flex;padding: 10px 14px 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" version=\"1.1\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"45px\" height=\"13px\" viewBox=\"0 0 450 130\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"插图\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(220,60,54)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(237,108,96)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"225\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(218,151,33)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(247,193,81)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"400\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(27,161,37)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(100,200,86)\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></ellipse></svg></span><code style=\"display: -webkit-box;padding: 0.5em 1em 1em;overflow-x: auto;text-indent: 0;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Menlo, Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, monospace;font-size: 90%;margin: 0;white-space: nowrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">from peft import LoraConfig, get_peft_model</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"># 配置LoRA</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">lora_config = LoraConfig(</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; r=16,</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; lora_alpha=32,</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; target_modules=[\"q_proj\", \"v_proj\", \"k_proj\", \"o_proj\", \"gate_proj\", \"up_proj\", \"down_proj\"], # 根据模型结构调整</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; lora_dropout=0.05,</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; bias=\"none\",</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; task_type=\"CAUSAL_LM\",</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; # modules_to_save=[\"embed_tokens\", \"lm_head\"] # 这是一个选项，可以让embedding层和输出层也参与训练</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">)</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"># 应用LoRA到模型</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">peft_model = get_peft_model(model, lora_config)</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">peft_model.print_trainable_parameters()</span></code></pre>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">注意</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：</span><code style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">modules_to_save</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">会让指定的模块（如embedding层）进行全参数微调，而不是LoRA微调。这对于新token是必要的，因为它们需要从头学习。LoRA则保护了其他层的权重。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">策略B：分阶段微调（如果不用LoRA）</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">如果你坚持全量微调（Full Fine-tuning），可以考虑一个“预热”阶段：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">1.</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">第一阶段</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：冻结模型绝大部分层，只训练embed_tokens和lm_head层。使用包含新token的语料进行少量步数的训练。这能让新token的embedding先“稳定下来”，找到一个比较合理的位置。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">2.</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">第二阶段</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：解冻所有层，进行完整的SFT。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">这种方法比直接全量微调要平滑，但比LoRA更耗资源且风险更高。</span></p>\n   <h1 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"padding:0px 1em;margin:2em auto 1em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:20.4px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;border-bottom:2px solid rgb(250, 81, 81);text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">总结与最佳实践</span></h1>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">1.</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">添加Token</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：使用</span><code style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">tokenizer.add_special_tokens</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">2.</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">调整模型大小</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：使用</span><code style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">model.resize_token_embeddings</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">3.</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">智能初始化（关键）：强烈推荐使用所有旧token embedding的均值来初始化新token的embedding</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">。这是效果和简便性之间最好的平衡。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">4.</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">高效微调（关键）：强烈推荐使用LoRA进行SFT</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">。它能有效防止灾难性遗忘，将训练的“火力”集中在任务适应和新token学习上，而不是破坏原有知识。确保SFT数据中充分、正确地使用了这些新token。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">5.</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">数据质量</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：确保你的SFT数据格式统一，新添加的special_token被正确地用作结构分隔符。模型需要通过大量高质量的样本来学习它们的“语法”功能。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">6.</span><strong style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">评估</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：在SFT后，不仅要评估模型在目标任务上的表现，还应该在一些通用的基准（如MMLU、C-Eval）上进行测试，以检查模型的通用能力是否出现大幅下降。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">遵循以上策略，你就可以在SFT阶段平稳地引入</span><code style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 90%;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">special_token</span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">，同时最大程度地保留大模型强大的基础能力</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章详细阐述了在 LLM 微调中添加特殊 Token 时，如何通过智能初始化 Embedding 和采用 PEFT（如 LoRA）策略，最大程度保留模型原有性能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章详细阐述了在 LLM 微调中添加特殊 Token 时，如何通过智能初始化 Embedding 和采用 PEFT（如 LoRA）策略，最大程度保留模型原有性能。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了在大型语言模型（LLM）的监督式微调（SFT）阶段添加特殊 Token（如`<|user|>`、`<|assistant|>`）时，如何避免对模型原有性能造成严重影响。核心问题在于新添加的 Token 在词向量矩阵（Embedding Matrix）和输出层（LM Head）中缺乏预训练向量，导致随机初始化产生的“噪声”会破坏模型通用知识，引发“灾难性遗忘”。文章提出了系统性策略：首先向 Tokenizer 添加新 Token 并调整模型 Embedding 大小；最关键的是，推荐使用所有旧 Token Embedding 的均值来初始化新 Token 的 Embedding，以实现语义上的“中性”平滑融入。其次，强烈推荐使用 PEFT（如 LoRA）进行微调，通过冻结大部分原始权重，将训练重心放在新 Token 用法和任务适应上，有效防止灾难性遗忘。文章提供了详细步骤、代码示例和最佳实践，旨在帮助开发者在引入新 Token 的同时，最大化保留 LLM 的强大基础能力。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "随机初始化新 Token 的 Embedding 和 LM Head 是导致模型性能下降的核心原因",
      "explanation": "新 Token 的随机向量与预训练的语义向量不匹配，会产生巨大梯度震荡，破坏模型预训练的通用知识，引发灾难性遗忘。"
    },
    {
      "point": "使用现有 Token Embedding 的均值初始化新 Token 的 Embedding 是最佳实践",
      "explanation": "这种方法能将新 Token 放置在语义空间的中心，提供“中性”的起始点，有效减少对模型原有知识的冲击，实现平滑融入。"
    },
    {
      "point": "采用 PEFT（如 LoRA）进行微调能有效保留模型通用能力并学习新 Token 用法",
      "explanation": "LoRA 通过冻结大部分原始模型权重，仅训练小型适配器，将训练火力集中于新 Token 和任务适应，最大程度避免灾难性遗忘。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "强烈推荐使用所有旧 token embedding 的均值来初始化新 token 的 embedding",
    "新添加的 token 在模型的词向量矩阵（Embedding Matrix）和输出层（LM Head）中没有对应的、经过预训练的向量，它们是\"从零开始\"的，这会给模型带来巨大的扰动。",
    "让新 token 的初始状态尽可能\"平滑\"地融入现有模型，并通过高效的微调方式让模型\"温柔\"地学会其用法。",
    "LoRA 通过在模型的线性层旁边增加小型的、可训练的\"适配器\"矩阵来进行微调，而原始模型的绝大部分权重保持冻结。",
    "确保你的 SFT 数据格式统一，新添加的 special_token 被正确地用作结构分隔符。模型需要通过大量高质量的样本来学习它们的\"语法\"功能。"
  ],
